    • Method Detail

      • getCircle

        public static javafx.scene.shape.Circle getCircle()
        Factory method for javafx.scene.shape.Circle
        Returns:
        a javafx.scene.shape.Circle object with center coordinates at default position (0,0), radius 75px, filled in white and outlined in red

      • getRectangle

        public static javafx.scene.shape.Rectangle getRectangle()
        Factory method for javafx.scene.shape.Rectangle
        Returns:
        a javafx.scene.shape.Rectangle object with upper left corner in default position (0,0), width and height 150px, filled in white and outlined in red. The corners are rounded.

      • getRandomShape

        public static javafx.scene.shape.Shape getRandomShape()
        Factory method for javafx.scene.shape.Shape
        Returns:
        a javafx.scene.shape.Shape object, either a Circle or a Rectangle. The Circle or Rectangle that is returned will have the properties as described in the methods getCircle() or getRectangle().
